---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Get Started · Ennea Evolution"
  description="You don't have to have it figured out to begin. The first step is a conversation: short, free, and honest."
>
  <!-- PANEL 1 · white · hero -->
  <section class="panel">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h1>Get Started</h1>
      <h3 style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">You don't have to have it figured out to begin.</h3>
      <p class="lead">That's true whether you're coming for yourself or for your team. The first step is a conversation, and it's an easy one: short, free, and honest.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="hairline-gold" />

  <!-- PANEL 2 · white · two labeled lanes, numbered steps -->
  <section class="panel">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2 lanes">
        <div>
          <h3>For you</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li><strong>Reach out.</strong> A few sentences about what's going on is plenty. "I don't know where to start" counts.</li>
            <li><strong>We talk.</strong> A free fifteen-minute consultation, no pressure and no obligation. You tell me what's happening, and I'll tell you honestly whether I can help. If I'm not the right fit, I'll say so and point you toward what is.</li>
            <li><strong>We begin.</strong> Sessions run fifty minutes to an hour, over Zoom for most clients, or in person in the Cache Valley, Utah area.</li>
          </ol>
          <p>Sessions are $125 to $190. I'm private pay and don't bill insurance. We'll cover the rest of the practical details in that first conversation.</p>
          <p>And for some seasons of life, weekly sessions aren't the right shape. If you need something more concentrated, ask me about it.</p>
          <a href="#reach-me" class="btn">Start the Conversation</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>For your team</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li><strong>Tell me what's going on.</strong> A team that's stuck, managers stepping into more, a culture you want to build. Email works fine.</li>
            <li><strong>We talk it through.</strong> I'll ask about your team, your goals, and what's been tried. Then I'll tell you honestly whether I can help.</li>
            <li><strong>You get a plan.</strong> What we'd do, what your team receives, and what it costs. One workshop or a year-long partnership. I travel throughout Utah, Idaho, and parts of Colorado for team trainings.</li>
          </ol>
          <a href="#reach-me" class="btn">Let's Talk</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="hairline-gold" />

  <!-- PANEL 3 · white · contact -->
  <section class="panel" id="reach-me">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <h3>Reach me</h3>
      <form name="get-started" method="POST" data-netlify="true" class="form-grid" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="get-started" />
        <div>
          <label for="gs-name">Name</label>
          <input id="gs-name" type="text" name="name" required autocomplete="name" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="gs-email">Email</label>
          <input id="gs-email" type="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="gs-interest">I'm interested in</label>
          <select id="gs-interest" name="interest">
            <option>Personal Work</option>
            <option>Professional Work</option>
            <option>Not sure yet</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="gs-message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="gs-message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn">Send</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .lanes { gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem); align-items: start; }
</style>
